得走，可以通过中介或者委托律师办理，省掉中介佣金。这么做要便宜很多，一般万把块钱就能搞定。 「本人直卖，省十多万中介费」！越来越多业主开始自己卖房了 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-90dbba5a062696895dba45b74982d392_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/645653207"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI+rzt5ZLdt+9sEAMaCTEwNTc1NjExNyDWl+WuBjAAOK0IQCtyCTY0NTY1MzIwN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1708856217.219834", "card_id": "Q_645768682", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 7}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "杭州一快速路上发生伤人事件，双方系表兄弟，有经营纠纷，如何看待此事？遇到矛盾该如何控制情绪、合理解决？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "浙江杭州警方通报网传宾利车主伤人：嫌疑人被刑拘，两人系表兄弟 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/645768682"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+rzt5ZLdt+9sEAMaCTEwNTc4MTc2MCCl4+quBjAAOA9ALHIJNjQ1NzY4NjgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1708856217.220286", "card_id": "Q_644495661", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 56}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价短剧《我在八零年代当后妈》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-c63a37ff44693db0a78e243511442bdd_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/644495661"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI+rzt5ZLdt+9sEAMaCTEwNTQ5ODgxNyDMtruuBjAAOI4BQC1yCTY0NDQ5NTY2MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1708856217.220501", "card_id": "Q_643098214", "feed_specific"